nd of up to  or  of nonatc atm surcharges monthly the adirondack trust company is an independent locally owned and operated community bank offering a wide variety of business and personal financial services the bank has more than  billion in assets and twelve branch offices the bank offers banking trust insurance and investment management services and originates real estate mortgages both residential and commercial and commercial business loans throughout its primary market area the bank is a bauer  star rated superior bank the banks website is adirondacktrustcom  the adirondack trust company  broadway saratoga springs ny    adirondacktrustcom sharing and personal tools please select the service you want to use newsvine digg delicious stumbleupon technorati buzz favorites google reader public link please use the above public link if you want to share this noodl on another website close smartlinks  adirondack trust company  finance  stock markets  security markets  stock markets  security markets  company news  financial services  banking  telecommunications services  banks  otc markets  back  view original format copyright  public technologies inc  privacy policy  terms of use  contact discover quality insurance in saratoga springs glens falls  albany ny  commercial small business  personal insurance  adirondack trust homecontact usprivacy noticelocations hours atms login to  webwise online banking webwise banking trust services credit cardonline access open an account online  broadway saratoga springs ny  phone  languages   deutsch  español    english   search about uspresidents welcomebank officialsboard of directorsexecutive vice presidentssenior management teamassistant vpsassistant treasurersnewsannual reportsquick factslocations hours atmscontact us holiday scheduletv commercialsplaces to visit in saratogaonline  mobile bankingloginebill payopen account onlinewebwise mobile bankingmobile check depositpersonal bankingchecking accountsbasic bankingregular checki