um balance requirements no monthly maintenance fee and a refund of up to  or  of nonatc atm surcharges monthly the adirondack trust company is an independent locally owned and operated community bank offering a wide variety of business and personal financial services the bank has more than  billion in assets and twelve branch offices the bank offers banking trust insurance and investment management services and originates real estate mortgages both residential and commercial and commercial business loans throughout its primary market area the bank is a bauer  star rated superior bank the banks website is adirondacktrustcom  the adirondack trust company  broadway saratoga springs ny    adirondacktrustcom adirondack trust company published this content on  may  and is solely responsible for the information contained herein distributed by public unedited and unaltered on  june   utc original documenthttpwwwadirondacktrustcomenaboutusnewstheadirondacktrustcompanyannouncesnewstudentcheckingproduct public permalinkhttpwwwpublicnowcomviewbbcaecdcec  latest news all news p mastercard  global payment cards top bn target bnn in  p cisco  warns of destruction of service attacks p us patents awarded to inventors in connecticut july  p nuance communications  us patents awarded to inventors in illinois july  p skyworks  us patents awarded to inventors in maryland july  p skyworks  us patents awarded to inventors in iowa july  p charles river laboratories intl  us patents awarded to inventors in new jersey july  p schneider electric  us patents awarded to inventors in north carolina july  p saint gobain  us patents awarded to inventors in ohio july  p lockheed martin  federal contracts awarded by federal agencies in georgia july  latest news all news advertisement most read news speedway motorsports inc  speedway motorsports inc schedules  second quarter earnings conference call mccowan and associates ltd  press release expedia inc  expedia  southcentral pa lands a spot on expedia